POC adding doctype declaration to opensocial gadgets in Liferay.
DictypeInjectionFilter write html5 doctype declaration to response output before main content from gadget xml specification is written.

Filter declaration should be registered in \webapps\opensocial-portlet\WEB-INF\liferay-web.xml
Before "Shindig Filter" section add following code of filter declaration:
    <filter>
        <filter-name>DoctypeInjectionFilter</filter-name>
        <filter-class>com.trizetto.liferay.filters.DoctypeInjectionFilter</filter-class>
    </filter>

Before "Shindig Filter" mapping declaration add following mapping:
    <filter-mapping>
        <filter-name>DoctypeInjectionFilter</filter-name>
        <url-pattern>/gadgets/ifr</url-pattern>
    </filter-mapping>

Restart Liferay.